column2: select   p.cModelMag_g-p.extinction_g as cModelMag_g,p.cModelMag_r-p.extinction_r as cModelMag_r,p.cModelMag_i-p.extinction_i as cModelMag_i,p.cModelMag_z-p.extinction_z as cModelMag_z,   p.cModelMagErr_g,p.cModelMagErr_r,p.cModelMagErr_i,p.cModelMagErr_z,   p.petroMag_g,p.petroMag_r,p.petroMag_i,p.petroMag_z,petroMagErr_g,petroMagErr_r,petroMagErr_i,petroMagErr_z   into cModel_petroMag    from PhotoObjALL as p join SpecObjALL as s    on p.specObjID=s.specObjID join galSpecline as l   on p.specObjID=l.specObjID    where s.scienceprimary=#
